title: Rainbow Six Siege - Official Deimos Operator Gameplay Overview Trailer
description:
With the new Operation Deadly Omen Update making its way to Rainbow Six Siege, players can now play as the masked antagonist Deimos. Take a look at the gameplay overview for Deimos whose kit includes the DeathMark gadget, a unique custom scope, and his deadly Vendetta revolver. Operation Deadly Omen is launching on March 12 for PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series S|X, and PC.
